    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206685</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">The Liberty Bell: From Obscurity to Icon</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Freiheit Bell: Von Obscurity zu Ikone</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La Liberté Bell : De l'obscurité au 
graphisme</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">A Liberdade Bell: Do obscurity ao ícone</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Libertà Bell: Da obscurity all'icona</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Το κουδούνι ελευθερίας: Από το σκοτάδι στο 
εικονίδιο</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">La Libertad Bell: De oscuridad al icono</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">helps students analyze -- through maps, readings, and images -- the historical and cultural influences that shaped the symbolic meaning of the Liberty Bell.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Hilfen Kursteilnehmer analysieren -- durch Karten,
Messwerte und Bilder -- die historischen und kulturellen Einflüsse, 
die die symbolische Bedeutung der Freiheit Bell formten.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">les étudiants d'aides analysent -- par des 
cartes, des lectures, et des images -- les influences historiques et 
culturelles qui ont formé la signification symbolique de la liberté 
Bell.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">os estudantes das ajudas analisam -- com os mapas,
as leituras, e as imagens -- as influências históricas e cultural 
que deram forma ao meaning simbólico da liberdade Bell.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">gli allievi di aiuti analizzano -- con i 
programmi, le letture e le immagini -- le influenze storiche e 
culturali che hanno modellato il significato simbolico della libertà 
Bell.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">βοηθά τους σπουδαστές να αναλύσουν -- μέσω των 
χαρτών, των αναγνώσεων, και των εικόνων -- τις ιστορικές και 
πολιτιστικές επιρροές που διαμόρφωσαν τη συμβολική έννοια του 
κουδουνιού ελευθερίας.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">los estudiantes de las ayudas analizan -- con 
correspondencias, lecturas, e imágenes -- las influencias históricas
y culturales que formaron el significado simbólico de la libertad 
Bell.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          <keyword>
